data.description: Look no further as opportunity awaits for you in downtown Key West. 1015 Packer Street is a legal duplex in old town on a spacious 4,562 square foot lot. The front home is a 1 bed/1 bath with an office space and a large open living room. The rear home is a 1 bed/1 bath with privacy. Both homes are surrounded by native plants and fruit trees with room for a pool, an addition or off street parking.  Both homes have the potential to make it your own. Located near Duval Street, art galleries, restaurants and so much more, this location is ideal for walking and biking to all that Key West has to offer and so much more. Don't miss out on this gem today!
